    public class WitnessTree<L,​AP>
extends CompactUniversalGraph<WitnessTreeState<?,​L,​?,​AP>,​String>
    A tree-like Graph that represents the BFS-style exploration of the tableau generated by the WitnessTreeExtractor. Edges may represent the extraction of inner subformulae, procedural calls/returns to/from other procedures, or actual steps in the transition system (modal nodes).
